'''Sarlain Star Press''' was a publishing company known for its anti-[[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] stance. This company published [[Madelein Aurin]]'s book ''[[Heroes Of The Republic]]'', which was eventually banned by [[Galactic Empire/Legends|the Empire]].

